    CHECK YOUR SHIPPING ADDRESS prior to submitting the 
    order. 
    

        Orders will be shipped to the address you specify, if that address is 
        incorrect, your order may be delayed 
        
        Returned orders will be reshipped at your expense. 
        
        We'll try to correct the address if you send it to us, but we 
        do get SO MANY orders with incorrect addresses it is hard 
        to keep track of which is which, so your best shot is to give us your 
        correct address to begin with. 
    


